     unbroken across the May–Aug shaded columns instead of letting it bleed
     through. (border-left colour is set inline in JS → override with !important.) */
  .tl-bar.dim {
    background: var(--bg);
    border-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--border) 45%, var(--bg));
